\i0 \ul Note on 3 Hour Forecast:\ulnone \
- User can click on a particular day in the table displaying the daily weather forecast (note that the click must be on the actual day and not anywhere in the row of that day) and another table will appear below displaying the 3 hour forecast for the next 24 hours from the day selected.\
- User can click on a different day in the daily forecast table to show the 3 hour forecast for that day.\
- User can click on anywhere on the table for the 3 hour forecast table to hide the table.\
